01.10 F N=0,999;D 2;D 4
01.20 Q

02.10 S A=0
02.20 S B=N
02.30 S C=FITR(B/10)
02.40 S A=A+(B-C*10)
02.50 S B=C
02.60 I (-B)2.3

03.10 S B=1
03.20 S B=B*10
03.30 I (B-M)3.2,3.2
03.40 S B=B/10
03.50 S M=M-FITR(M/B)*B

04.10 S P=N
04.20 S M=P
04.30 I (M-A)4.4,4.9,4.4
04.40 D 3
04.50 I (M)4.3,4.6,4.3
04.60 S P=FITR(P/10)
04.70 I (P)4.2,4.8,4.2
04.80 R
04.90 T %3,N,!
